  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add chopped onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add minced garlic and grated ginger; sauté for another minute.",
    "Add chopped Scotch bonnet peppers, ground allspice, and dried thyme.",
    "Add the callaloo leaves and stir well to combine.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk and single cream; bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Reduce heat to low and let the stew cook for 20 minutes, or until the callaloo is tender.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve hot, garnished with chopped scallions if desired."
